cs.NE, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SI, cs.SY 

Reasoning: 
1. cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) - The paper focuses on analyzing the memory capacity of a type of neural network called the echo state network (ESN). 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) - The paper proposes two deep ESN architectures and evaluates their performance in terms of prediction accuracy. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper proposes novel deep ESN architectures and evaluates their performance in terms of memory capacity and prediction accuracy. 
4. cs.SI (Signal Processing) - The paper deals with analyzing the performance of a neural network in processing input sequences and generating output sequences. 
5. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper proposes deep ESN architectures for improving the prediction accuracy of a system and analyzes their memory capacity.
